	<span style="font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;line-height:2;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;6、用XP3 Viewer解压提取</span>
</p>
<p>
	<span style="font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;line-height:2;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;7、用xp3文件提取器提取</span>
</p>
<p>
	<span style="font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;line-height:2;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;xp3是galgame的data的一种封装类型，一般内封CG、voice、bgm等。像FSN还有AB2社的游戏基本上是用xp3封装。</span>
</p>
<h2>
	<span style="font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;line-height:2;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="color:#E53333;font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;line-height:2;">问：XP3viewer用win7怎么打开?</span></strong>
